      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWIFT BREE (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from six tries. Comes off a (30.75) win last time, scoring by 1.5 lengths in a NG over 527m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. ZIPPING BERKELEY (8) was fifth in a Grade 5 two back then found trouble in the run and took a tumble at this track last time. May be worth another try. JUNGLE TIGER (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (31.31) in a NG at this track. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and three minor placings from seven starts. Should be thereabouts. IMPERIAL AUDREY (4) can sneak into the finish again.",
